{"tid":85751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死2隻]瘋男失控鎚殺鄰居2男童","createTime":"2017-01-18T14:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T15:52:04.000Z","uid":32407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bcbfae3f91b11d77bd3fe42b179af2c9bf870b5f","tid":85751,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170118/56188082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170118%2F56188082&d=RVlam78G7dsTti9aOdoEZ5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=967366a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170118%2F56188082&h=dfc91fc5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170118/56188082</a><br />\n<br />\n廣州花都區炭步鎮發生命案。一名男子前日早上7時40分許，持鐵鎚殺害鄰居兩名男童後潛逃，警方已發出1萬元人民幣懸賞通緝。<br />\n<br />\n警方透露，花都區炭步鎮鴨一村某輪胎廠宿舍發生一宗命案，湖南藍山縣的33歲疑犯曾兵有重大犯案嫌疑。炭步鎮居民稱，疑犯持鐵鎚將鄰居家的2名孩子砸死，包括一名2歲的男童以及一名13歲男孩。據報，當日曾兵拿着手工用的鎚子進入鄰居房間，把來串門的2歲男童當場擊斃，13歲男童被擊至重傷，送院後傷重不治。男童母親也被擊至頭顱凹陷重傷，「都是直接往頭上砸，太殘忍了！」<br />\n曾兵行兇後逃跑，其60多歲父母當時不在家，後來被警方傳召協助調查。據街坊稱，遇遇危運的肖姓一家與疑兇同樣來自湖南，住在該處多年，兩夫婦都在附近工廠打工，事發時丈夫也在家中。<br />\n13歲兒子遇害後，其父對當時情景仍歷歷在目，當日與妻子正坐在桌旁吃早飯，兒子在裡屋睡覺，房間的門虛掩着。曾兵突然進來，懷裡揣着鐵鎚，甚麼都不說就開始砸人。自己的妻子重傷，鄰家2歲男童被砸死，13歲的兒子從裡屋跑出來，衣服都沒穿好，也慘遭毒手。他形容曾兵當時像發瘋似了，他上前阻止但還是沒能阻止悲劇發生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7e24818461c87c5e9969b54ac119e1610be2fc","tid":85751,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:31:51.000Z","msg":"係咪成日喺度大叫 迫到隔離發顛"},{"pid":"1c1faf8890106d89b53d4a0e249845e91882c8da","tid":85751,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:35:23.000Z","msg":"曾兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解支那佬改得出咁柒嘅名"},{"pid":"850716d3b782a14273d37dec3e33c2885530cdc3","tid":85751,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87fce646f471068661fa521e3a2c8a09c259c94","tid":85751,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解支那佬改得出咁柒嘅名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那文化水平係咁上下"},{"pid":"18ae15fdc2c9a88158ca6db8c8f35d7be46ead55","tid":85751,"uid":24358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:17:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解支那佬改得出咁柒嘅名</blockquote><br />\n我仲以為佢打錯字啊仆街 諗撚左勁耐"},{"pid":"8d94ce6441a170054143447607e613840b4e7f52","tid":85751,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>曾兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解支那佬改得出咁柒嘅名</blockquote><br />\n我仲以為佢打錯字啊仆街 諗撚左勁耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n增兵"},{"pid":"0452817948ffb6f096e1ac77579cc51cbd352b6a","tid":85751,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"唔知點解覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b364159ccd26645c62b1b99a1d634a32528852b9","tid":85751,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>曾兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解支那佬改得出咁柒嘅名</blockquote><br />\n我仲以為佢打錯字啊仆街 諗撚左勁耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n增兵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢老豆改名果陣打緊杖唔夠打要援軍所以改個仔做曾兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}